<plot>Brooke Carey wants to buy a horse for her ten-year-old daughter, Samantha, but has had no experience with horses. During their search for the ideal horse, Brooke and Samantha encounter many of the pitfalls often experienced by the novice horse-buyer. Through their experiences, the potential first horse-owner is shown how to go about buying the right horse.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503871</url></doc>
